      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOLLY MISS (2) boasts strong form at this distance having won three times from four starts. In the money last time at Gunnedah (24.83) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 2.5 lengths second. Looks a key chance on best form. KIARNI PHOENIX (1) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by one length at this track in a handy 30.71 beating ZIPPING LYNDY. Draws the cherry and goes well over this trip. Shapes as a top winning chance on latest effort. MODEST MAN (3) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last four runs. Last start finished 2nd in a NG on March 21 over 515m at The Gardens behind Kenzie Robbo beaten a neck (29.64). Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Racing well and deserves a win. WEFFALEE LEE LEE (5) scored by 5.5 lengths last time (29.58) in a Grade 4/5 over 515m at The Gardens. Unbeaten in two runs from this draw.",
